{"tid":581212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[千軍萬馬來相見]19歲女PO文免費約炮　3千人衝現場參戰","createTime":"2018-03-05T06:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T08:51:55.000Z","uid":120541,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12e4ea32422110b3cd5a0c9f0a07e3bb473a0285","tid":581212,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"中國一名暱稱「千金怡怡」的女網友，日前在《微信》發文指出，「誰來找我...打炮...免費....6316」，並補充「一天不做就....難受」，並公布了酒店位置，該篇發文隨即在網路上瘋傳，甚至傳出有3000千人到場，最後酒店報警處理，將女子帶走。<br />\n<br />\n3月1日晚上，一位19歲網路暱稱為「千金怡怡」的網友，在微信發文約炮，誰來找我...打炮...免費....6316」，並補充「一天不做就....難受」，並公布地點是在海南島三亞市的希爾頓酒店，而6316就是房間號碼。此篇貼文瞬間在網路上瘋傳，《微信》上稱有3000人到場共襄盛舉，暱稱為「秦岭二月」的網友，也在《微博》分享影片說，「此刻我正在去三亞6316的路上，可是千金怡怡葉郡怡被趕出酒店。沒想到一篇發文吸引了上千網友到場，讓千金怡怡嚇得再度發文，「我都要哭了，別傳播了，我真的只是開玩笑阿」。<br />\n<br />\n據《中國新聞網》報導，三亞公安局指出，日前一女子葉某在微信朋友圈發布公開招嫖資訊，造成惡劣影響，警方依法對涉案行為人處以行政拘留15日並處罰款。而女子被抓並非網友報警，而是涉事酒店主動報案，酒店稱葉某發布了招嫖資訊，並附帶房間號和酒店定位，讓許多民眾到酒店敲該房間房門，並有大量陌生人打酒店電話，嚴重影響了酒店的正常運營。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場後發現，該房的客人已經退房離開，過連夜偵查後於3月2日在三亞鳳凰國際機場某酒店將葉某逮捕，葉某指出，她發文後害怕被公安機關查處，於當日刪除，在遭遇大量陌生人敲門後感到害怕，就要求酒店立刻護送其離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/145445_918739631da3f9e6b32a7548014b5e4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F145445_918739631da3f9e6b32a7548014b5e4d.jpg&h=96d079ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/145447_ed0b2fe55a95d3f2cd312d09b0399711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F145447_ed0b2fe55a95d3f2cd312d09b0399711.jpg&h=cd6b5ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180304/1308053/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180304%2F1308053%2F&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3ffiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=197cd5aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180304%2F1308053%2F&h=7ae2e8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180304/1308053/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/164838/-%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%9E6136-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85-%E5%8D%83%E9%87%91%E6%80%A1%E6%80%A1-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%88%BF%E8%99%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%B4%84%E7%82%AE-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%89%A3%E7%95%9915%E5%A4%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F164838%2F-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%259E6136-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E5%258D%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2580%25A1%25E6%2580%25A1-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%2582%25AE-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%2589%25A3%25E7%2595%259915%25E5%25A4%25A9&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3ffiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=eafc2a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/164838/-%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%9E6136-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85-%E5%8D%83%E9%87%91%E6%80%A1%E6%80%A1-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%88%BF%E8%99%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%B4%84%E7%82%AE-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%89%A3%E7%95%9915%E5%A4%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2355236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2355236&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3ffiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f586bc82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2355236&h=86d8ab60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2355236</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/145622_0902b6a12bb7e8bd7149189baaef50b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F145622_0902b6a12bb7e8bd7149189baaef50b8.jpg&h=2f9ecef3&s={SI